metadata.name: VAGABOND
metadata.description:
"How many month is it? 3...5... could be almost a year.  I don't even care about it anymore. I'm tired of fighting and running away, but I have no other choices. I don't even have a place to return to.. and those soldiers... they're hunting me down. 

...To be honest, I just don't care anymore."

"..."

"I better keep going."
